title: pbe Can not get in
body: This account is currently inactive. Please contact Player Support for further information at support.riotgames.com

replies.body: Looking into this, I wasn't able to see a PBE account tied to the account you're posting from.  If you do have one on another account, reach out to us in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so our account team can help out!
